-- British Warship Destroys Pirate `Whaler' Off Coast of Somalia, NATO Says
-- B y   A l a r i c   N i g h t i n g a l e
-- 2010-11-24T11:03:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-24/british-warship-destroys-pirate-whaler-off-coast-of-somalia-nato-says.html
A British warship destroyed a pirate
vessel off the coast of Somalia, the North Atlantic Treaty
Organization said.  The frigate  HMS Montrose  destroyed the “whaler” after its
helicopter spotted the craft anchored at a “known camp” for
pirates, NATO said in an e-mailed  statement  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
